On behalf of our client CBRE are pleased to offer for lease an A Grade office facility located within the Jandakot Business Park known as Jandakot City.

CBRE see this offering as an extremely rare opportunity for a business to lease First Class commercial buildings of the highest standard.

Flexibility is the key with this offering with various sizes available to suit a variety of needs.

Businesses can lease a smaller portion with the ability to grow in the future.

LOCATION 
Just 15 minutes from the Perth CBD, via the Kwinana Freeway and Roe Highway, Jandakot City is ideally located for ease of access for tenants and their customers.

Jandakot City is located at the entrance to Jandakot Airport and both precincts operate independently of each other. There is direct access off Roe Highway onto Karel Avenue which leads into Jandakot City from the east and north east suburbs, as well as easy entry onto the Kwinana Freeway (1km) which is the main north / south road transport route.


The vision for Jandakot City is an integrated commercial and industrial park occupied by high calibre tenants residing in first rate buildings owned by Jandakot City.


Please contact the exclusive agent to obtain further details and inspection.
